  "subject": "Import TOSCA data_types defined in VSP",
  "commit_message": "Import TOSCA data_types defined in VSP\n\nImport TOSCA data_types defined in a VSP, storing it inside\nthe vertex metadata, so the data type is a private resource\nfor the created VF.\nAdds a new package with new data types declaration\n(unknown to SDC) to be tested by the sdc-tests-api.\n\nChange-Id: I6e96a4aef99cdaa4f8af8f5d656d56154de89441\nIssue-ID: SDC-2764\nSigned-off-by: André Schmid <andre.schmid@est.tech>\n",
